* Task Execution\nPatterns
** Serial Execution
***_ Tasks run sequentially
***_ Safer for dependent data
***_ Slower overall
** Parallel Execution
***_ Independent tasks run simultaneously
***_ Reduces total job duration
***_ Requires more compute
** Compute Sharing
*** Shared Compute
****_ Same cluster for related tasks
****_ Reduces startup latency
****_ Shared memory/CPU
*** Dedicated Clusters
****_ Isolated resources
****_ For resource-intensive tasks
** Balance
***_ Parallelism vs. compute capacity
***_ Workspace concurrency limits
@endmindmap
